Package enteties

Class StudentTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • enteties.StudentTest
  • public class StudentTest
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a student test. This class stores information about a student's test, including the student's ID, test code, time passed, answers, grade, lecturer notes, approval status, and change reason. It also contains additional attributes that are not stored in the database, such as the student's name, the test to execute, and the test itself. The class provides various constructors to create different instances of a student test object.
